<sentence ID="SENT-2" start="140" end="286"><ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">U.S</ENAMEX>. and <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">British</ENAMEX> troops were <Event TYPE="Movement" SUBTYPE="Transport">moving</Event> on the strategic southern port
