<sentence ID="SENT-7" start="661" end="831">Earlier Saturday, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Baghdad</ENAMEX> was again <Event TYPE="Conflict" SUBTYPE="Attack">targeted</Event>, one day after a massive
